Package: lightgraph
Type: Package
Title: High-Performance HTML Canvas-Based Network Visualization
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hao", "Zhu", email = "haozhu233@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Donna", "Slonim", email = "donna.slonim@tufts.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Description: A lightweight R binding for lightGraph network visualization using
    HTML canvas for high-performance rendering. This package provides an htmlwidget
    interface for visualizing networks from adjacency matrices.
